<div role="region" aria-label="Anchor card for the sound k, spelled c, like the word cat" class="mx-auto mb-4 max-w-2xl rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-orange-50 border-2 border-amber-300 shadow-md overflow-hidden transition-all">
